---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The TRIZ Advantage | PIVOT Management Consultants" description="When Lean Six Sigma hits a wall, TRIZ dissolves the trade-off. Structured innovation adopted by Fortune 500 companies worldwide.">
  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-brand font-semibold mb-2">When Lean Six Sigma hits a wall</p>
      <h1 class="text-[1.75rem] sm:text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] text-ink max-w-2xl">
        Lean reduces variation. TRIZ removes the trade-off.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-ink-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        TRIZ (pronounced "trees") is a Russian acronym meaning "the theory of inventive problem solving." When trial-and-error and brainstorming fail to solve complex challenges — and when Six Sigma and Lean reach their limits — TRIZ offers a structured framework for breaking through seemingly impossible obstacles.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Example: The Wall → TRIZ → Result -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-surface-alt border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-6">How it works — a real example</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-muted font-semibold mb-2">The Wall</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">
            Coating must be thicker for durability AND thinner for cost/weight. LSS can optimise one — not both.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-5 border-2 border-brand">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-brand font-semibold mb-2">TRIZ Move</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">
            Separate the contradiction in space/structure — not a spec compromise. Inventive principles reveal a path LSS doesn't have.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-muted font-semibold mb-2">Result</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">
            Both requirements met. LSS locks in the gain. Your team owns the method for the next contradiction.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why TRIZ -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-6">Why TRIZ — not just more Lean Six Sigma</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-lg p-5 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">LSS optimises within constraints</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">Reduce variation, eliminate waste, control the process. Powerful — until the gains flatten.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-5 bg-brand-light border border-brand/20">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">TRIZ eliminates the constraint</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">Structured inventive principles dissolve the contradiction itself. The system moves to a new level.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Adopted by -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-14 bg-surface-alt border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-4">Adopted by Fortune 500 companies</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-4">TRIZ has proven effective at organisations including:</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs font-medium text-ink-muted">
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">Boeing</span>
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">Ford</span>
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">3M</span>
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">Procter & Gamble</span>
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">Samsung</span>
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">Siemens</span>
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">LG Electronics</span>
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">Motorola</span>
        <span class="bg-surface rounded px-3 py-1.5 border border-border">Cummins</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Workshop -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2">TRIZ Fast-Trak Workshop</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-5">A one-day intensive that equips your team with structured innovation methods.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-lg p-5 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-2">What you'll learn</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-light space-y-1">
            <li>- Solution patterns that predict breakthroughs</li>
            <li>- Why systematic logic surpasses intuition</li>
            <li>- Scaling strategies from prototype to production</li>
            <li>- Accelerated testing methodologies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-5 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Curriculum</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-light space-y-1">
            <li>- Ideal Final Result identification</li>
            <li>- Resource analysis (materials, energy, information)</li>
            <li>- 40 principles for addressing trade-offs</li>
            <li>- Separation principles for inherent contradictions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2">Is your program ready for TRIZ?</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-5">Find out in 4 minutes with the Breakthrough Diagnostic.</p>
      <a
        href="/diagnostic"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 bg-brand text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-dark transition-colors"
      >
        Take the Diagnostic &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
